text: Němeček (feminine Němečková) is a Czech surname, meaning "a small German". It is a diminutive of Němec, meaning "a German". Notable people include: * Bohumil Němeček, Czech boxer * Jan Němeček, Czech ice hockey player * Lenka Němečková, Czech tennis player * Libor Němeček, Czech tennis player * Svatopluk Němeček, Czech politician * Václav Němeček, Czech footballer Category:Czech-language surnames
title: Němeček
